headline: Roku and Texas Roadhouse have been highlighted as Zacks Bull and Bear of the Day
summary: Roku jumps after a double-beat quarter with rising ads and raised guidance, while Texas Roadhouse struggles under mounting commodity inflation.

headline: Ralph Lauren Introduces Latest Artists in Residence with Polo Ralph Lauren x TÓPA Collaboration
summary: NEW YORK, November 18, 2025--Ralph Lauren (NYSE:RL) today launched Polo Ralph Lauren x TÓPA, the fourth collaboration of the Company's Artist in Residence program. The collection blends the distinctive cultural elements of Indigenous-led clothing brand, TÓPA, with the timeless signature style of Polo Ralph Lauren. The products are offered within Polo Ralph Lauren’s Fall/Holiday 2025 collection.
